    <h1>Abhigyan Sharma</h1>
    <h2>Senior Inventive Scientist, AT&amp;T Labs Research</h2>
    <h3>E-mail: [my first name]@research.att.com</h3>
    <p>I am a researcher at <a href="http://www.research.att.com">AT&amp;T Labs
        Research</a> in the <a href="http://about.att.com/innovation/labs/cloudqos">CloudQos</a>
      research group. I completed my PhD in <a href="https://www.cs.umass.edu/">Computer
        Science at UMass Amherst</a>&nbsp; <a href="https://www.cics.umass.edu/speakers/abhigyan/2015/jul/28">in
        2015</a> under the fantastic supervision of <a href="http://people.cs.umass.edu/%7Earun/">Arun
        Venkataramani</a> and <a href="http://people.cs.umass.edu/%7Eramesh/">Ramesh
        Sitaraman</a>. I am currently working on cloud computing research
      related to <a href="http://www.att.com/Common/about_us/pdf/AT&amp;T%20Domain%202.0%20Vision%20White%20Paper.pdf">Network
        Functions Virtualization</a>.</p>
